playstore_details.title: JobStack | Worker
playstore_details.description:
Work the way you want to work. When you want to work.

The JobStack Worker Mobile App – powered by PeopleReady - gives you the ability to see jobs in your area that match your skills. You can take a job with a simple swipe or tap. After you've taken a job, you will receive information on where to go, what to bring and what to expect once you arrive. Rate your workday and confirm hours.

JobStack requires you to be registered to work as a PeopleReady employee.

Key features:
• Login with the phone number we have on file
• View and take jobs that match your preferences and profile
• Edit your travel preferences and profile
• Receive clear instruction on where to go and what to bring
• See your work hours approved by the customer
• View job site on a map
• Rate the jobs you work

Not yet registered through PeopleReady?

Download the app and we’ll walk you through the application and onboarding process!

PeopleReady is the largest industrial staffing company in North America and provides customers with the best match of dependable, hardworking employees.
playstore_details.summary: The JobStack Mobile App for Workers.
playstore_details.summaryHTML: The JobStack Mobile App for Workers.
playstore_details.recentChanges:
Improvements
We updated error messages to be more informative for you on the following pages:
- Login
- Forgot password
- Change Cell number
- Registration (PIN page)

Bug Fixes
- Submit Ratings and Hours: in a very rare case submitting hours was failing. That issue was fixed.
- After registration, the Call Now button is now operational. In some edge cases the button was not working.
- Notification Center: the Load More feature is now displayed only when there is more content to read
playstore_details.recentChangesHTML:
Improvements
We updated error messages to be more informative for you on the following pages:
- Login
- Forgot password
- Change Cell number
- Registration (PIN page)

Bug Fixes
- Submit Ratings and Hours: in a very rare case submitting hours was failing. That issue was fixed.
- After registration, the Call Now button is now operational. In some edge cases the button was not working.
- Notification Center: the Load More feature is now displayed only when there is more content to read
